  "storyboard_markdown": "# Scene Contract: CH001_SC003\n\n## Production Intent\nEstablish the physical threat of the Apache warriors through a transition from quiet observation to high-intensity combat. The sequence must move from a wide, observational perspective in the valley to a tight, chaotic handheld skirmish on the plateau.\n\n## Required Cast\n- John Carter (Younger)\n- apache_warriors (Large group, traditional 19th-century attire, wielding arrows)\n\n## Required Environments\n- Arizona hills/plateau (including remote gold-bearing quartz vein and narrow cliffside trail)\n- High plateau Apache camp\n\n## Continuity Constraints\n- Total count of apache_warriors must remain consistent during skirmish.\n- Direction of pursuit from valley to plateau must be linear.\n- Weapon handling: rifles/sidearms for Carter, arrows for warriors.\n\n## Beat List\n- BT001: Detection of movement in the valley.\n- BT002: Pursuit along the narrow cliffside trail.\n- BT003: Chaotic skirmish at the Apache camp on the plateau.",
